--- !u!114 &1336340733
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1336340731}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 48fdfcc8a67199e4aa51c8e7b7b14715, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WitcherRightVersion.Dialogue.DialogueInteractable
  displayName: Marta Lozovaya
  interactionPrompt: Talk
  startNodeId: start
  returnToElderNodeId: 
  completedQuestNodeId: 
  dialogueNodes:
  - Id: start
    SpeakerName: Marta Lozovaya
    Body: 'So Voytsekh sent you south. Good. Walk with open eyes: black slime, torn
      reeds, tracks too heavy for a man.'
    Choices:
    - Text: I took the contract. What should I look for?
      NextNodeId: tracks
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: marta_spoken
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Why does the swamp remember the dead?
      NextNodeId: curse
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Later.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: tracks
    SpeakerName: Marta Lozovaya
    Body: Look for claw cuts, poisoned slime, and cloth caught on the reeds. When
      all three agree, draw silver.
    Choices:
    - Text: Then I start with the tracks.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
    - Text: Tell me about the curse.
      NextNodeId: curse
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
  - Id: curse
    SpeakerName: Marta Lozovaya
    Body: People blame Elsa because a single witch is easier than a village full
      of liars. Survive the monster first; truth comes later.
    Choices:
    - Text: I will inspect the swamp.
      NextNodeId: tracks
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: marta_spoken
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Enough for now.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
